                  <div id="breadcrumb"><h2 class="element-invisible">You are here</h2><div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> » <a href="/about">About</a> » <a href="/about/deliverables">Deliverables</a></div></div>
          
    
    <div id="content" class="column"><div class="section">
            <a id="main-content"></a>
                    <h1 class="title" id="page-title">
          6.1: BrightESS section on www.europeanspallationsource.se        </h1>
                          <div class="tabs">
                  </div>
                        <div class="block-system-main" >
  
  <div class="node node-deliverable node-full view-mode-full   contextual-links-region">
    <div class="field field-name-post-date">Nov 20, 2015</div><div class="field field-name-work-package deliverable-full-work-package"><div class="block-views-deliverables-block-1" >
  
  <div class="view view-deliverables view-id-deliverables view-display-id-block_1 view-dom-id-8edf2915435a3665d484114f8f7b8b40">
          <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last">
      
  <div class="views-field views-field-title">    <span class="views-label views-label-title">Work package: </span>    <span class="field-content"><a href="/about/work-packages/work-package-6-collaboration-communication-and-dissemination">Work Package 6: Collaboration, Communication and Dissemination</a></span>  </div>  </div>
          </div>
</div>
</div><div class="field field-name-body"><p>The BrightnESS website serves as the core dissemination tool and the central portal for all project related communication activities. The BrightnESS website is set up as a subsection of the ESS website in order to leverage the existing traffic and thus help to raise awareness about the project.</p>
<p>This approach also allows the visitors to navigate easily to the ESS website, which provides detailed information about the next generation research facility standing at the very center of this project.</p>
<p>The website is available in English as this is the working language of the consortium of partners. Moreover, content provided in English will help to reach out to large audiences from different countries. The website will be continuously updated through the duration of the project.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>DOI: <a href="https://doi.org/10.17199/BRIGHTNESS.D6.1" rel="nofollow">https://doi.org/10.17199/BRIGHTNESS.D6.1</a></p>
</div><div class="field field-name-field-attachment deliverable-full-attachment"><div class="label-above">Downloads:&nbsp;</div><span class="file"><img class="file-icon" alt="PDF icon" title="application/pdf" src="/modules/file/icons/application-pdf.png" /> <a href="https://brightness.esss.se/sites/default/files/deliverables/Deliverable%20Report%20D6.1%20Brightness%20section%20on%20ESS%20website_0.pdf" type="application/pdf; length=651891">Deliverable Report D6.1 Brightness section on ESS website.pdf</a></span></div></div>
</div>
            

    </div></div> <!-- /.section, /#content -->

